00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:11,680
 I'll sign up. Let me share a piece of information. 

21
00:02:11,680 --> 00:02:17,700
 A WeChat user named Lily with bamboo avatar claims to have an exclusive remedy for ALS. 

22
00:02:17,700 --> 00:02:21,240
 This guy is a scammer. My sister was scammed out of 40,000 yuan (~$5,534). 

23
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:24,120
 Her condition has become more serious. 

24
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:27,340
Please do not easily believe online treatment information.

25
00:02:27,340 --> 00:02:32,040
Seek legitimate medical help and report scams to police.

26
00:02:34,300 --> 00:02:37,040
 These heartless scoundrels! 

27
00:02:37,040 --> 00:02:39,020
 ALS is incurable. 

28
00:02:39,020 --> 00:02:40,840
 How can they deceive terminally ill patients? 

29
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:43,860
 - How to persuade my dad to have a tracheotomy? 
 - Is there really no way to cure it? 

30
00:02:43,860 --> 00:02:46,440
 I am willing to trade my life for my wife's. 

31
00:02:46,440 --> 00:02:51,040
 My husband, You Xiaojun, passed away at 4:15 a.m. today. 

32
00:02:51,040 --> 00:02:54,500
 I'll donate the sputum suction machine to a fellow patient in the group. 

33
00:02:54,500 --> 00:02:57,860
 If anyone needs it, PM me your address, and I'll send it to you. 

34
00:02:57,860 --> 00:03:00,700
 Thank you for your help over the past three years. 

35
00:03:00,700 --> 00:03:03,620
 Thank you, Uncle Guo and Xiao Lin. 

36
00:03:04,160 --> 00:03:08,880
May Brother Xiaojun rest in peace. Ms. You, please accept my condolences.

37
00:03:09,420 --> 00:03:13,544
 May there be no illness in heaven, my condolences.  
    

38
00:03:13,544 --> 00:03:17,840
 Thank you all. I've contacted the recipient. 

39
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:21,700
 I compiled three years of nursing care for Xiaojun into a document. 

40
00:03:21,700 --> 00:03:25,560
 I'm sharing it in hopes of helping more patients. 

41
00:03:26,140 --> 00:03:29,892
 Wishing you all the best, never give up hope.  
    

42
00:03:36,660 --> 00:03:41,340
   
   

43
00:03:43,100 --> 00:03:44,860
 How is it? Comfortable, right? 

44
00:03:44,860 --> 00:03:47,020
Feels good.

45
00:03:47,020 --> 00:03:49,020
Let's try this one.

46
00:03:49,780 --> 00:03:53,880
You can't just run home and ask your parents for money every time.

47
00:03:53,880 --> 00:03:56,500
Well, we are married and adults.

48
00:03:56,500 --> 00:03:58,640
Be mature, okay?

49
00:03:58,640 --> 00:04:01,100
But we really don't have money, do we?

50
00:04:01,100 --> 00:04:03,740
Without money, we can't offer help.

51
00:04:04,600 --> 00:04:08,680
Can't we just earn money? We are healthy grown-ups. And we have jobs.

52
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:12,480
Though Lin Tuo is ill, he can still draw design sketches and earn money.

53
00:04:12,480 --> 00:04:15,440
Lin Tuo can do it because he has skills.

54
00:04:15,440 --> 00:04:17,540
He can earn money with his skills.

55
00:04:17,540 --> 00:04:20,560
I have no skills or specialties.

56
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:22,840
Well, neither do you.

57
00:04:22,840 --> 00:04:25,180
We are useless.

58
00:04:25,180 --> 00:04:27,400
Get up, you're useless, not I.

59
00:04:27,400 --> 00:04:30,620
- I... 
 - I can live stream, that's my skill.

60
00:04:32,020 --> 00:04:34,420
Can it be used for fundraising?

61
00:04:34,420 --> 00:04:37,340
Why not ask netizens to donate money?

62
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:43,940
That's not impossible. Come on, massage me.

63
00:04:44,700 --> 00:04:46,340
But we can't be so blunt, right?

64
00:04:46,340 --> 00:04:52,180
You can't just tell them to donate money to save a child.

65
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:56,300
Why would strangers donate money to us?

66
00:04:56,300 --> 00:05:01,340
Then do something meaningful.

67
00:05:01,960 --> 00:05:03,990
Something meaningful?

68
00:05:06,720 --> 00:05:08,680
Xiao Ye said he contacted the student union.

69
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:12,440
They can initiate a school donation campaign with authentic medical cases.

70
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:16,880
I did organize some previously. I can send him the ones I have on hand first.

71
00:05:16,880 --> 00:05:18,740
All right.

72
00:05:18,740 --> 00:05:20,580
Our project is also ready.

73
00:05:20,580 --> 00:05:22,520
Yes, that's right.

74
00:05:22,520 --> 00:05:24,060
What project is it?

75
00:05:24,060 --> 00:05:26,800
We'll be livestreaming the Ice Bucket Challenge.

76
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:30,180
Xindi has contacted various famous influencers. They will join our live stream by then.

77
00:05:30,180 --> 00:05:35,080
We've reached an agreement with the platform. All profits obtained from the Ice Bucket Challenge Charity Sale

78
00:05:35,080 --> 00:05:39,140
will be donated to the foundation for Dong Dong's medical expenses.

79
00:05:39,140 --> 00:05:43,160
There's more, and we've also reached an agreement with the factory to sell at cost price.

80
00:05:43,160 --> 00:05:47,820
Actually, we went to negotiate with a try-and-see attitude. But they were so supportive.

81
00:05:47,820 --> 00:05:49,260
This is all we can do.

82
00:05:49,260 --> 00:05:51,400
This is already pretty impressive.

83
00:05:51,400 --> 00:05:53,840
You two will do this together?

84
00:05:53,840 --> 00:05:55,560
He will.

85
00:05:57,260 --> 00:05:59,480
I'll be cheering for him.

86
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:03,360
Honey, you can do it. Look how strong you are. Just some cold water, you'll be fine.

87
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:06,000
No problem, I believe in you. I love you.

88
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:08,860
- Going to the canteen? 
 - Yes.

89
